5. Entertainment Free:Children’s Playground (09:00–18:00), Recreation Room and Table Tennis (09:00–22:00);
Paid Services: Indoor Badminton Court: RMB55/hour; Automatic Mahjong Room: RMB30/hour; Basketball Court: RMB180/hour/Half-Court;
6. Settlement of Accounts:
(1) Please transfer RMB5,000 to the hotel’s corporate account in advance to secure rooms and meeting venues; (2) A valid ID is required for check-in. Upon check-in, a deposit of RMB21,000 must be paid to receive the room key; (3) All charges must be settled at check-out, and the hotel will provide the corresponding invoice; (4) Hotel Name: Guangzhou Guangbai Lianhua Mountain Hotel Co., Ltd.; Bank: Guangzhou Panyu Asian Games City Branch, Industrial and Commercial Bank of China;
Account Number: 3602225219000028285
